{"tid":2139321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"颱風黑格比登陸浙江造成嚴重破壞","createTime":"2020-08-04T08:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T12:32:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":433,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"039a93da5659589bb177edbc91fd2f7daf2e5415","tid":2139321,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:03:24.000Z","msg":"颱風黑格比登陸浙江造成嚴重破壞<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-08-04 15:25<br />\n<br />\n颱風黑格比凌晨在浙江溫州樂清市沿海登陸，是16年來首個登陸樂清的颱風。浙江廣泛地區出現狂風暴雨，溫州沿海翻起巨浪，有居民深夜被強勁的風雨聲吵醒，並感覺住所在搖晃。多處有山泥傾瀉，道路水浸，有礦區被洪水沖毀，水庫溢滿，大片農場受損。<br />\n<br />\n黑格比登陸後強度將逐漸減弱，穿過浙江及江蘇後，明日由江蘇北部移入黃海西部。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2350479&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=77b19607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350479</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7406d7fdf40b46880e76d3cc6ddc0492526ab9dd","tid":2139321,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97928a8f95e4efbed8f3d099d789e640e1cbeb32","tid":2139321,"uid":108337,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"Fake news, 信政府唔驚"},{"pid":"4ceb45cde33aedd810d1b97eb2e4c56f0